data.description: BUY THE MODEL HOME! This Hamilton B is almost 3500 Square feet of luxury. Home comes with upgraded Enhanced Vinyl Plank Floors in the living area, upgraded quartz counterswith admiral blue 42' cabinets with Soft Close. This is the last home we offer in Parkview with the Gourmet kitchen options which includescook top with ex tra cabinets and a wall unit microwave/oven combo. Home has a the optional owners to retreat that gives the master suite extra space and flexibility. Home also has a extra Flex space perfect for a at home gym or a theatre room. Home also has a guest room with its own en-suite perfectfor when guests visit. Dont forget about the walk in tile shower with rainhead faucet and huge closet in the master and last but not least home has a 25x11 Lanai.
